Comment: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:33.34,Song,,0,0,0,,I always see your smile, whenever I look into the past.
Comment: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:38.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the day when I stood still after a draining walk...
